fine 
meanwhile bush campaign staffers have been told to do nothing 
to keep alive the rumors about dukakis mental health after bush 
himself wondered whether some of the information was coming from 
his campaign according to his chief of staff craig fuller 
he asked me the question fuller said i have no reason to 
believe we have any of our people behind it 
fuller said campaign manager lee atwater gathered the bush staff 
together wednesday and admonished everybody to stay out of this 
story stay out of the rumor business 
george bush doesnt want us involved in that kind of a 
story fuller said one of the troublesome aspects of a 
presidential campaign is that a rumor takes off and has a life of 
its own i dont know what the reality is but i figure its up to 
somebody else besides us to find out 
on another subject fuller confirmed that treasury secretary 
james a baker iii would resign his post to become chairman of the 
bush campaign before the start of the gop convention on august 15 
bakers plans to join the campaign have been widely reported 
and previously confirmed by sources in both the bush campaign and 
the reagan administration 
sources have said that reagan would nominate new york investment 
banker nicholas brady to serve out the remainder of bakers term 
and that the announcement could come as early as friday 
however fuller said there still is no lock on the exact day 
for bakers job switch 
at the news conference bush predicted that he would win texas 
his adopted state despite the presence on the democratic ticket 
of vice presidential candidate sen lloyd bentsen of texas 
the race is between george bush and michael dukakis in 
texas he said i am going to spend what it takes and be here 
as long as it takes to win texas 
he said he hopes to win the hispanic vote even though he 
doesnt speak spanish as dukakis and bentsen do 
it isnt whether you can speak spanish its what is in your 
heart bush said he dukakis can speak spanish but i have 
the heartbeat bush then repeated his oftenused reference to his 
three grandchildren who are part mexicanamerican 
